Tidak. Awak nak tahu sebabnya?

660
00:46:41,173 --> 00:46:43,509
Sebab kisah sedih awak selalu jual itu.

661
00:46:43,592 --> 00:46:46,553
Apa yang bagusnya menderita
sebab mak pekerja bar?

662
00:46:46,637 --> 00:46:48,639
Hei, Choi Jae-hee!

663
00:46:48,722 --> 00:46:52,059
- Hei, ulang sekali lagi.
- Ini benda betul.

664
00:46:52,142 --> 00:46:54,811
Awak jual cerita sedih
supaya orang kasihan!

665
00:46:55,646 --> 00:46:57,189
- Ulang semula!
- Tunggu.

666
00:46:57,981 --> 00:47:00,484
Orang tak suka awak.

667
00:47:00,567 --> 00:47:02,361
Mereka cuma kasihankan awak.

668
00:47:02,903 --> 00:47:04,488
- Tak guna!
- Ra-ik!

669
00:47:04,571 --> 00:47:06,406
