Ingat ada artis undangan.

684
00:49:06,693 --> 00:49:09,363
Sepatutnya ada,
tapi mereka bergaduh semalam.

685
00:49:09,446 --> 00:49:12,658
Saya kerja semalam,
nampak Ra-ik dan Jae-hee bergaduh.

686
00:49:12,741 --> 00:49:15,577
Mereka datang untuk konsert dia
dan dia buat begini?

687
00:49:15,661 --> 00:49:16,495
Sikap dia teruk.

688
00:49:17,162 --> 00:49:18,455
Apa maksud mereka?

689
00:49:20,332 --> 00:49:22,668
Penyebaran berita palsu akan didenda…

690
00:49:22,751 --> 00:49:23,669
MESEJ

691
00:49:26,338 --> 00:49:27,422
LIKE

692
00:49:28,131 --> 00:49:29,466
Awak nampak komen itu?

693
00:49:31,093 --> 00:49:32,469
